metadata.name: Star Dreams Girls Token #1
metadata.description: Congrats on being the Star Dreams girl's agent in the Metaverse! There's a meet and greet coming up, are you ready to meet the Star Dreams girls ? At a fan meeting, you get to see the Star Dreams girls up close and even get a handshake or an autograph! Do you really looking forward to have the merch as soon as possible? It would also have the opportunity to get up close and personal with Star Dreams girls on special festivals!
